				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Loan-Loan/Bi-gi%C3%A0-t%E1%BB%A9-ph%C3%A1ch-%C4%91%E1%BB%87-t%E1%BB%A9-ph%C3%A1ch/poem-SI4NDuCyqx32JJT6xWqouw">Bi già tứ phách - đệ tứ phách - 悲笳四拍－第四拍</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tri%E1%BB%87u-Loan-Loan/author-37QNViodCzbNj28eS0C3jA">Triệu Loan Loan</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/Chi%C3%AAu-Qu%C3%A2n-t%E1%BB%AB-k%E1%BB%B3-2/poem-N2bpFZiYmRzWawDj_nm2bQ">Chiêu Quân từ kỳ 2 - 昭君詞其二</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/B%E1%BA%A1ch-C%C6%B0-D%E1%BB%8B/author-GTDxHQP8eUITUxph4otjnA">Bạch Cư Dị</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/D%E1%BB%A5-ch%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%B3-t%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-h%E1%BB%8Bch-v%C4%83n/poem-j9Hfw5Qp2ojck3M3yZbHSw">Dụ chư tỳ tướng hịch văn - 諭諸裨將檄文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BA%A7n-Qu%E1%BB%91c-Tu%E1%BA%A5n/author-B3gaZnYZj3Y7n162MsC6mQ">Trần Quốc Tuấn</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/D%E1%BB%AF-S%C6%A1n-Nam-Th%C6%B0%E1%BB%A3ng-Hi%E1%BB%87p-tr%E1%BA%A5n-quan-Tr%E1%BA%A7n-H%E1%BA%A7u-x%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Bng-ho%E1%BA%A1-k%E1%BB%B3-6/poem-HFkCK1vP4elAdvAy9bFjKw">Dữ Sơn Nam Thượng Hiệp trấn quan Trần Hầu xướng hoạ kỳ 6 - 與山南上協鎮官陳侯唱和其六</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/H%E1%BB%93-Xu%C3%A2n-H%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author-PBy92bBuBMMs53v9tc9E0A">Hồ Xuân Hương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ti%E1%BA%BFp/Ho%C3%A0n-gia-h%C3%A0nh/poem-WLCej6p8joS9S2UtQ5cdRQ">Hoàn gia hành - 還家行</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-Ti%E1%BA%BFp/author-fRO_gR-Wik2vy4vMMbBfSg">Trịnh Tiếp</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/Ho%C3%A0ng-%C4%91i%E1%BB%83u-2/poem-WO6fgcH0tDNdpBUPAr_qIg">Hoàng điểu 2 - 黃鳥 2</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaI